{"tid":1385151,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《嚴正呼籲》集中8 5罷工消息","createTime":"2019-07-30T04:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:53.000Z","uid":73317,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77d2afaf08bb04b3c374bd2e30b3c321004b299b","tid":1385151,"uid":73317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"相信咁多位連登仔 睇到今朝消息都好爽<br />\n但唔好唔記得 我地係連一個訴求都未達到<br />\n唔好困在連登世界 我都好想大家覺醒<br />\n罷工係每個人主動企出嚟 <br />\n不合作運動係一班勇敢嘅人的無聲吶喊 <br />\n亦會波及被動嘅「偽中立」市民<br />\n請大家認真諗下使唔使一個星期 都持續<br />\n唔係鬼 不分化不割蓆 只係大家獨立思考 <br />\n我點都支持你地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"3bccc27421ea27a5fd6e391b2354f2107320818f","tid":1385151,"uid":73317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆"},{"pid":"60c8f787bb7654467360f926ad8c9ab48f326578","tid":1385151,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>8月5日全港大罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"18fc96e5d1d86ff8ea662a366bf36352e1cb0c19","tid":1385151,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}